title: The Complete Carter Pewterschmidt Family Guy Timeline

media:group.media:title: The Complete Carter Pewterschmidt Family Guy Timeline
media:group.media:description:
In this video we look at the entire timeline of Carter Pewterschmidt from Family Guy. Voiced by Seth Macfarlane, we look at Carter's entire life history, his past and future. Taking a look at the Family Guy cutaways, as well as the full Family Guy episodes, I've put Carter Pewterschmidt's life in chronological order. From season 1 to newest Family Guy season.
I go into Carter's evoltuion in Family Guy, from his marriage with Babs, his daughter Lois, as well as his relationship with Peter Griffin.

We also look at the funniest Family Guy moments from Peter, Lois, Chris, Meg and Brian. As well as other Family Guy characters from Quahog Rhode Island.

Script Written By: Michael McCarrick
